data.title: What Philip Glass And Tommy Tutone Have In Common
data.meta_description: Jim Keller manages a famous minimalist composer. He co-wrote "867-5309/Jenny" with Tommy Tutone. And somewhere in between, he's released his third solo album, Heaven Can Wait.
